Read the 404error.php sources to get info about installing
these files.

You should be able to move the website/errors directory
into your website/ directory and alter your httpd.conf
or .htaccess file to get the desired effect.

To cause auto-generation of newswire files, just go into
the newswire directories and delete the files.  As the
files get accessed, the resultant 404 errors will trigger
regeneration.


